Package br.com.riziko.ncs.core.model.segment Description

################################################################################## This directory must contain classes for representing Nato Codification System Segments that exist to keep Codification data organized. The definition of which data belongs to which Segment and why it is important is under ACodP-1 document (2017), chapter Five. source: www.nato.int/structur/AC/135/acodp1/ACodP1_E.pdf ##################################################################################

Rogerio
